                  <summary>I) Gospel of John (fols. 3ra-84va) &#xD; - Bǝsrāta Yoḥannǝs “Gospel of
                     John” (fols. 3ra-83vb)&#xD; - Short postscript (fols. 83vb-84rb)&#xD; - List of
                     the “tituli” for the Gospel of John: 20 tituli (fols. 84rb-84va)&#xD; &#xD;
                     Additiones 1-3.</summary>
